---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Group By (CSV) - GigaSieve Recipe" description="Group a CSV by a column and count rows in the browser.">
    <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-3xl">
        <nav class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">
            <a href="/recipes" class="hover:text-emerald-400">Recipes</a>
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
            <a href="/recipes" class="hover:text-emerald-400">Csv</a>
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400">Group By (CSV)</span>
        </nav>

        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-200 mb-4">Group By (CSV)</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">
            Need a quick summary by category, country, or status? Group by a column locally.
        </p>

        <a href="/app" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-cyan-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/30 hover:shadow-emerald-500/50 transition-all mb-8">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
            Open in App
        </a>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">How it works</h2>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                <li>Open a CSV in GigaSieve.</li>
                <li>Pick the column to group by (e.g., country).</li>
                <li>Counts appear in the Insights panel.</li>
                <li>Sort to find the top groups.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Sample Input and Output</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm font-mono">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-2">Input</p>
                    <pre class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg text-slate-400 overflow-x-auto">country,amount
US,100
KR,40
US,55</pre>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-2">Output</p>
                    <pre class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg text-slate-400">US: 2
KR: 1</pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-400 mb-2">Tip</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
                For large CSVs, group by low-cardinality columns for best performance.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Related Recipes</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
            <a href="/recipes/csv/top-values" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800 transition-all">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Column Top Values</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">Top values</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/recipes/csv/filter-rows" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800 transition-all">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Filter Rows</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">Narrow results</p>
            </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-300 mb-4">Related Guides</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="/guides/csv-group-by-in-browser" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800 transition-all">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">CSV Group By in Browser</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">Step-by-step</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/guides/open-1gb-csv-in-browser" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800 transition-all">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Open 1GB CSV</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">Large files</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
